		*DATE AND TIME DATA TYPES FORMAT

DATE : (YYYY-MM-DD)
TIME : (HHH-MM-SS)
YEAR : (YYYY)

*to create database -> CREATE DATABASE ajey ;
*to delete database -> DROP DATABASE ajey ;

*to display structure of table -> DESC ajey ;


*if we want to create duplicate table -> CREATE TABLE ajey2 AS SELECT *FROM ajey;
*if we want to duplicate particular fields -> CREATE TABLE ajey2 AS id, name, age FROM ajey;


---ALTER---

*(ADD) if we want to add new column to the table  -> ALTER TABLE ajey ADD address VARCHAR(30);
*or if we want to add new column after specific colum then we have to use AFTER ->  ALTER TABLE ajey ADD address VARCHAR(30) AFTER age;
*to add column at first -> ALTER TABLE ajey ADD address VARCHAR (10)  FIRST;


MODIFY 

*to change constraints size ex. VARCHAR(10) TO VARCHAR(20), WE CAN ALSO APPLY KEY ->  ALTER TABLE ajey MODIFY  name VARCHAR(20) PRIMARY KEY;
























